Welp guys! IT looks like we're in luck! Not only have we gotten one of the BIGGEST comic book movie crossovers with Marvel's Avengers Endgame, but now thanks to Lamb of God, we're finally getting to see Mathew Perry from Friends square off against Pennywise the dancing clown. Maybe I interpreted that all wrong. This could just be another fucking game in the series of Mortal Kombat with Johnny Cage vs Mileena. Fuck idk anymore!
